OPTIONS,v 1.2 1994/02/12 02:43:43 shigeya Exp

Current Options of distribute/archive program


-a ALIASID		set alias-id

-d			debug on
-e			add errors-to
-f sender		set sender
-h hostname		hostname of this machine (if you want it to be generic)
-i			always ignore reply-to and add mine
-j			use majordomo style file layout

-l listname		mail-list-name
-m sendmail_opt		set additional option to sendmail
-n news_from		remove incoming mail's news-to-mail style header
-o 			use owner-, instead of -request
-q			add x-sequence
-r reply-to		set reply-to addr
-s			do smart about add-me mail
-t			terse processing (no Subject alias)
-u userid (*)		set mailer user id
-v seqfile		add sequence

-x			write INDEX file


-A accept-addr-file	set accept addr file
-B bracedef		set subject tag open/close
-C archive-path		set archive path
-D debug		forward debug output to console.

-F footer		include footer file after mail body

-H header		include header file before mail body
-I seqfile		add sequence

-L recipient		Recipient file
-M mailing-list-name	same as: -e -a NAME -r NAME -v NAME -A NAME -l NAME
-N mailing-list-name	same as: -e -a NAME -v NAME -A NAME -l NAME
-P precedence		set precedence: header

-R 			zap recieved-by header

-U userid (*)		set archive user id
-V 			print version

-X			remove version header
-Y archive_path		set archive base path
-Z index_file		set index file name
